snippet.title: The Expanse: A Telltale Series - First Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Go behind the scenes with the dev team and actress Cara Gee!

This quick look shows some of the new gameplay we're using to tell the story of Camina Drummer in 
The Expanse: A Telltale Series. 

You will enter The Expanse July 27th 2023, beratna! 

#TheExpanse #Expanse #telltalegames 

Wishlist the Game Now ►
